These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goldfish, turtle, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
3. the owner of the goldfish is not to the left of the owner of the turtle##8
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Pet   | turtle | goldfish | fish | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
City: venice, rome, berlin, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to venice is not to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
2. the person traveling to rome is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person traveling to berlin##2
3. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| City   | venice | berlin | rome | san-francisco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-3::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, poker, backgammon, monopoly
1. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person playing monopoly##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |   2   |   3    |   4    |
| Game   | scrabble | monopoly | poker | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, motorbike, bike, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##7
2. the person driving the skateboard is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8
3. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person driving the car##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |       3       |   4    |
| Transport   | motorbike | skateboard | bike | car |

