2. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the person watching drama movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2   |    3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | drama | time-travel | documentary |

